all right, lets get started.<br>
<br>
Free People<br>
-First we have gwemegil which, is of course gonna beef arwen up or sacrifice it if there is a very strong minion bothering you.Asfaloth is gonna help us a lot too.<br>
<br>
-The bow of galadhrim will stregthen legolas or help you a lil bit with direct damage.<br>
